{"name":"Lake.Build.Imports","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lake.Build.Index"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dcccfb73cb247e9478220375ab7de03f7c67e505/src/lake/Lake/Build/Imports.lean#L40-L59","name":"Lake.buildImportsAndDeps","line":40,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lake/Build/Imports.html#Lake.buildImportsAndDeps","doc":"Builds an `Array` of module imports. Used by `lake setup-file` to build modules\nfor the Lean server and by `lake lean` to build the imports of a file.\nReturns the set of module dynlibs built (so they can be loaded by Lean).\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lake/Build/Imports.html#Lake.buildImportsAndDeps\"><span class=\"name\">Lake</span>.<span class=\"name\">buildImportsAndDeps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(imports : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lake/Config/Module.html#Lake.Module\">Lake.Module</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lake/Build/Fetch.html#Lake.FetchM\">Lake.FetchM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lake/Build/Job.html#Lake.BuildJob\">Lake.BuildJob</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/System/FilePath.html#System.FilePath\">Lake.FilePath</a></span>)</span></span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/dcccfb73cb247e9478220375ab7de03f7c67e505/src/lake/Lake/Build/Imports.lean#L20-L33","name":"Lake.recBuildImports","line":20,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lake/Build/Imports.html#Lake.recBuildImports","doc":"Recursively build a set of imported modules and return their build jobs,\nthe build jobs of their precompiled modules and the build jobs of said modules'\nexternal libraries.\n"},"